Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Budget cuts continue
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xgr8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Jan 1985
Reagan's election promises on spending will be overtaken by Congress ready to trim more from proposed budget. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less